data.description: New Listing LOCATION says it all!. This farmhouse style home is surrounded by beautiful homes in a country setting and is a diamond-in-the-rough waiting for a new buyer with a vision to make this home a beautiful place to live. This property features a 3 bedroom home and a detached 2 car garage set on 30,504 sq feet of gently sloping land surrounded by beautiful New England stone walls and bordering town owned conservation land. Call today to make an appointment to see this property!
